FARE UPDATE
August 20, 1982
Subject to change without notice. Subject to government approval.
FARES P/F/Y/Y2 SHOWN ONE WAY. ALL OTHER FARES SHOWN ROUND TRIP
Fare Rules: Refer to Air Tariff Book 2.
These fares are for travel originating in the U.S.A.
SOUTH AMERICA FOR $999.
From Los Angeles
From MIA $850.
From NYC $979.
This fare applies to BUE/SCL/RIO/MVD/ASU
1 - Stay requirement 7 day minimum/21 day maximum.
2 - Applicable on Aerolineas Argentinas only.
3 - Reservations and ticketing at least 21 days in advance.
4 - Minimum group size: 2 passenaers.
5 - IT number required.
6 - Land arrangements required: $150. for 6 nights plus $20 each additional night.
7 - 2 stopovers allowed. One in each direction plus point of turnaround. Additional stopovers: $25. each.
8 - Change and cancellation penalties will apply.
